<body data-gramm=""false"">I really hope you are pleased with your New Credit Choice results,<br />
~Please be sure to add me to your address book to continue to receive my emails. ~<br />
<br />
Rent is tough to pay when it is due, or at all, I barely made rent on time in November.<br />
Could be you got your hours at work cut down or worse you got laid off. What do you do? Stress out?<br />
I have been there, I was there last year and even this current month. This month it was just tough<br />
timing for me, last year it was much worse. I was really desperate, I did not sleep and I was getting threats from my<br />
landlord. In time I got caught up thank God, but it was months of stress barely dealt with.<br />
<br />
Today I found this great site offering information on both private and government assistance for rent and utilities, I<br />
wish I had found it years ago. You need to take a look and get the information you need, or wonder<br />
if one day you might!Just don&#39;t go through what I went through. Check out this site I found!<br />
I should say there isn&#39;t only help with rent, it can be for any bills you have!<br />
<br />
Especially as we are in the Christmas Season it is really the time to find help and get some breathing room<br />
<br />
<a href=""http://clicks.aweber.com/y/ct/?l=GFBwn&m=gfeJaAnGqtmFnBY&b=oukr258DwWLNsRpwt_QTAA"" target=""_blank"">Assistance With Rent And More</a><br />
<br />
As always, if you have questions please let me know. Or let me know how you like my recommendations!<br />
<br />
<br />
One last thing, when you are in a pinch you should still know your credit score. We really like Credit Sesame.<br />
It&#39;s free and no card is required! You should check it out. <a href=""http://clicks.aweber.com/y/ct/?l=GFBwn&m=gfeJaAnGqtmFnBY&b=Ad1j_gnL5TwAZFzXc9rRDg"">View your score here</a><br />
<br />
Thank you for your time,<br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
Patrick Carlson<br />

<body data-gramm=""false"">I do hope you have been pleased with your New Credit Choice results,<br />
~Please be sure to add me to your address book to continue to receive my emails. ~<br />
<br />
I have been going on about how you need to find out your credit score, and it is important!<br />
I found this site called Credit Sesame that gives it to you for free with out putting in a card. Amazing!<br />
You need to know your credit score. It is really the first step in getting access to cards, better loans,<br />
renting a better place and more! Even buying a home if you are hoping to do that.<br />
<br />
Then you have the next step, seeing your credit report. What&#39;s the difference you ask? Well the credit report<br />
will tell you all the issues on your credit report you need to address. So it is very important<br />
to get the report and deal with the people or companies on the report. Basically you need to find out<br />
who you need to talk to or call out as not being a real debt. The good news is you can get both for free!<br />
<br />
I did a lot of searching on this, and you should do. Check out the link below for both credit score and credit report.<br />
<br />
<a href=""http://clicks.aweber.com/y/ct/?l=GFBwn&m=hP7p5NPuqtmFnBY&b=x4mexm0PGfJLa46HIh7z1A"" target=""_blank"">View Your Score</a><br />
<br />
As always, if you have questions please let me know. Or let me know how you like my recommendations!<br />
<br />
Thanks you for your time,<br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
Patrick Carlson<br />
New Credit Choice

<body data-gramm=""false"">I do hope you have been pleased with your New Credit Choice results,<br />
~Please be sure to add me to your address book to continue to receive my emails. ~<br />
<br />
I have been going on about how you need to find out your credit score, and it is important!<br />
I found this site called Credit Sesame that gives it to you for free with out putting in a card. Amazing!<br />
You need to know your credit score. It is really the first step in getting access to cards, better loans,<br />
renting a better place and more! Even buying a home if you are hoping to do that.<br />
<br />
Then you have the next step, seeing your credit report. What&#39;s the difference you ask? Well the credit report<br />
will tell you all the issues on your credit report you need to address. So it is very important<br />
to get the report and deal with the people or companies on the report. Basically you need to find out<br />
who you need to talk to or call out as not being a real debt. The good news is you can get both for free!<br />
<br />
I did a lot of searching on this, and you should do. Check out the link below for both credit score and credit report.<br />
<br />
<a href=""http://clicks.aweber.com/y/ct/?l=GFBwn&m=hP7p5NPuqtmFnBY&b=x4mexm0PGfJLa46HIh7z1A"" target=""_blank"">View Your Score</a><br />
<br />
As always, if you have questions please let me know. Or let me know how you like my recommendations!<br />
<br />
Thanks you for your time,<br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
Patrick Carlson<br />

",,"I do hope you have been pleased with your New Credit Choice results,

~Please be sure to add me to your address book to continue to receive my emails. ~

I have been going on about how you need to find out your credit score, and it is important!

I found this site called Credit Sesame that gives it to you for free with out putting in a card. Amazing!

You need to know your credit score. It is really the first step in getting access to cards, better loans,

renting a better place and more! Even buying a home if you are hoping to do that.

Then you have the next step, seeing your credit report. What's the difference you ask? Well the credit report

will tell you all the issues on your credit report you need to address. So it is very important

to get the report and deal with the people or companies on the report. Basically you need to find out

who you need to talk to or call out as not being a real debt. The good news is you can get both for free!

I did a lot of searching on this, and you should do. Check out the link below for both credit score and credit report.

View Your Score

http://clicks.aweber.com/y/ct/?l=GFBwn&m=hP7p5NPuqtmFnBY&b=x4mexm0PGfJLa46HIh7z1A

As always, if you have questions please let me know. Or let me know how you like my recommendations!

Thanks you for your time,

Patrick Carlson

Rent is tough to pay when it is due, or at all, I barely made rent on time in November.<br />
Could be you got your hours at work cut down or worse you got laid off. What do you do? Stress out?<br />

timing for me, last year it was much worse. I was really desperate, I did not sleep and I was getting threats from my<br />

<br />

wish I had found it years ago. You need to take a look and get the information you need, or wonder<br />
if one day you might!Just don&#39;t go through what I went through. Check out this site I found!<br />
I should say there isn&#39;t only help with rent, it can be for any bills you have!<br />
<br />
Especially as we are in the Christmas Season it is really the time to find help and get some breathing room<br />
<br />

<body data-gramm=""false"">I really hope you are pleased with your New Credit Choice results,<br />
~Please be sure to add me to your address book to continue to receive my emails. ~<br />
<br />
Rent is tough to pay when it is due, or at all, I barely made rent on time in November.<br />
Could be you got your hours at work cut down or worse you got laid off. What do you do? Stress out?<br />
I have been there, I was there last year and even this current month. This month it was just tough<br />
timing for me, last year it was much worse. I was really desperate, I did not sleep and I was getting threats from my<br />
landlord. In time I got caught up thank God, but it was months of stress barely dealt with.<br />
<br />
Today I found this great site offering information on both private and government assistance for rent and utilities, I<br />
wish I had found it years ago. You need to take a look and get the information you need, or wonder<br />
if one day you might!Just don&#39;t go through what I went through. Check out this site I found!<br />
I should say there isn&#39;t only help with rent, it can be for any bills you have!<br />
<br />
Especially as we are in the Christmas Season it is really the time to find help and get some breathing room<br />
<br />
<a href=""http://clicks.aweber.com/y/ct/?l=GFBwn&m=gfeJaAnGqtmFnBY&b=oukr258DwWLNsRpwt_QTAA"" target=""_blank"">Assistance With Rent And More</a><br />
<br />
As always, if you have questions please let me know. Or let me know how you like my recommendations!<br />
<br />
<br />
One last thing, when you are in a pinch you should still know your credit score. We really like Credit Sesame.<br />
It&#39;s free and no card is required! You should check it out. <a href=""http://clicks.aweber.com/y/ct/?l=GFBwn&m=gfeJaAnGqtmFnBY&b=Ad1j_gnL5TwAZFzXc9rRDg"">View your score here</a><br />
<br />
Thank you for your time,<br />
<br />
<br />
<br />

<body data-gramm=""false"">I do hope you have been pleased with your New Credit Choice results,<br />
~Please be sure to add me to your address book to continue to receive my emails. ~<br />
<br />
I have been going on about how you need to find out your credit score, and it is important!<br />
I found this site called Credit Sesame that gives it to you for free with out putting in a card. Amazing!<br />
You need to know your credit score. It is really the first step in getting access to cards, better loans,<br />
renting a better place and more! Even buying a home if you are hoping to do that.<br />
<br />
Then you have the next step, seeing your credit report. What&#39;s the difference you ask? Well the credit report<br />
will tell you all the issues on your credit report you need to address. So it is very important<br />
to get the report and deal with the people or companies on the report. Basically you need to find out<br />
who you need to talk to or call out as not being a real debt. The good news is you can get both for free!<br />
<br />
I did a lot of searching on this, and you should do. Check out the link below for both credit score and credit report.<br />
<br />
<a href=""http://clicks.aweber.com/y/ct/?l=GFBwn&m=hP7p5NPuqtmFnBY&b=x4mexm0PGfJLa46HIh7z1A"" target=""_blank"">View Your Score</a><br />
<br />
As always, if you have questions please let me know. Or let me know how you like my recommendations!<br />
<br />
Thanks you for your time,<br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
Patrick Carlson<br />

<body data-gramm=""false"">I do hope you have been pleased with your New Credit Choice results,<br />
~Please be sure to add me to your address book to continue to receive my emails. ~<br />
<br />
I have been going on about how you need to find out your credit score, and it is important!<br />
I found this site called Credit Sesame that gives it to you for free with out putting in a card. Amazing!<br />
You need to know your credit score. It is really the first step in getting access to cards, better loans,<br />
renting a better place and more! Even buying a home if you are hoping to do that.<br />
<br />
Then you have the next step, seeing your credit report. What&#39;s the difference you ask? Well the credit report<br />
will tell you all the issues on your credit report you need to address. So it is very important<br />
to get the report and deal with the people or companies on the report. Basically you need to find out<br />
who you need to talk to or call out as not being a real debt. The good news is you can get both for free!<br />
<br />
I did a lot of searching on this, and you should do. Check out the link below for both credit score and credit report.<br />
<br />
<a href=""http://clicks.aweber.com/y/ct/?l=GFBwn&m=hP7p5NPuqtmFnBY&b=x4mexm0PGfJLa46HIh7z1A"" target=""_blank"">View Your Score</a><br />
<br />
As always, if you have questions please let me know. Or let me know how you like my recommendations!<br />
<br />
Thanks you for your time,<br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
Patrick Carlson<br />

",,"I do hope you have been pleased with your New Credit Choice results,

~Please be sure to add me to your address book to continue to receive my emails. ~

I have been going on about how you need to find out your credit score, and it is important!

I found this site called Credit Sesame that gives it to you for free with out putting in a card. Amazing!

You need to know your credit score. It is really the first step in getting access to cards, better loans,

renting a better place and more! Even buying a home if you are hoping to do that.

Then you have the next step, seeing your credit report. What's the difference you ask? Well the credit report

will tell you all the issues on your credit report you need to address. So it is very important

to get the report and deal with the people or companies on the report. Basically you need to find out

who you need to talk to or call out as not being a real debt. The good news is you can get both for free!

I did a lot of searching on this, and you should do. Check out the link below for both credit score and credit report.

View Your Score

As always, if you have questions please let me know. Or let me know how you like my recommendations!

Thanks you for your time,

Patrick Carlson
